      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCHWARZ (6) placed in his two Melton outings of last campaign, finishing runner-up in the Tatlow Stakes when fresh and only 1.6m away in a Breeders Crown heat before his prep ended early. That was 18 months ago but he should be ready to go after placing in two recent trials and his form stands out in this line-up. WOODVILLE FLYER (2) progressed off a debut fourth to come from wide on the back row and miss by just a head as runner-up at Kilmore last week. A good draw should see her perform well. SEASIDE LADY (3) was runner-up here two back before she led from this barrier and stuck on last start. Can be competitive. MAURLEN GRACE (1) has performed well from back row draws at her last two outings so should enjoy the ace draw.",
